  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy male and/or female (nonchildbearing potential) subjects between the ages of 18
             and 55 years, inclusive

          -  Body Mass Index (BMI) between 18 to 32 kg/m2, inclusive, and a total body weight &gt;45
             kg (99 lbs)

          -  Non-users of nicotine

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Evidence or history of clinically significant medical illness

          -  A history of seizures, including childhood febrile seizures

          -  Any condition possibly affecting drug absorption
      </textblock>
